The '''Super Transport VI''' was a [[Super Transport series]] container [[Starship/Legends|ship]] built by [[Kuat Drive Yards/Legends|Kuat Drive Yards]].

==History==
By the time of the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], the Super Transport VI was considered severely outdated, and had been almost entirely replaced by newer Super Transport models.

In [[7 ABY/Legends|7 ABY]], the damaged Super Transport VI [[Red Feathers|''Blood Nest'']] was located on [[Blood Nest]], a moon of the [[Gas giant/Legends|gas giant]] [[M2398]], and served as the base of operations for local pirates when they were defeated by [[Wraith Squadron]]. Later that year, the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] used the barely functional ''Blood Nest'', newly-renamed ''Red Feathers'', to transport three [[Squadron/Legends|squadrons]] of fighters during the [[Battle of Ession]], including [[Rogue Squadron/Legends|Rogue Squadron]].

